title: Producer Eddie Wrestles Our Co-Host + Coronavirus Talk With Dr. Kevin Lewis + Name The TV Theme Song Game
itunes:title: Producer Eddie Wrestles Our Co-Host + Coronavirus Talk With Dr. Kevin Lewis + Name The TV Theme Song Game
description:
Our final co-host fills in for Lunchbox. WWE Hall of Fame wrestler Jeff Jarrett takes us behind the scenes of wresting and even gets Eddie in a wrestling move! Dr. Kevin Lewis answers all of our questions about the coronavirus. Plus, a fun game guessing television show themes after only hearing the first line!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
